snippet.title: Amit Bhadana LL.B - Part 01 - Kalah (कलह) | Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Winzo app - https://winzo.onelink.me/VS3O/8ffc518c

Amit Bhadana presents Amit Bhadhana LL.B

From making videos with mobile phones to creating a film for YouTube, I have come a long way, and this journey wouldn't have been possible without your love and support. This is just the first step and sky is the limit.

Aa hi gayi vo tareekh jab katghare mein hazir hoga entertainment, aur is baat ki gavahi degi khud ye film. Jo dil ke saaf hote hai vo dimaag walon se haar jate hai, lekin Amit ke paas dono hain aur is chalaak duniya ke har daanv-pench ka tod le kar chalta hai ye dil aur dimag wala kamaal ka vakeel. Jab khud ko sabit karne Amit nikalta hai kanoon ki pathrili sadkon par to us ke hisse mein aate hain kuch atrangi case. Museebaton se ummeed nahi haarti, aur phir Amit ka sahara lene aati hai Ana, lekin kya ye raah hogi aasan?? Kyunki Amit ke samne hai kanoon ka diggaj Advocate Mehta.

snippet.title: Jetha से पहले Tapu और Gogi ने किया Bathroom पे कब्ज़ा |Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah|Sangram Ke Aam
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Watch the full episodes of Jetha & Sangram Ke Aam:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cRmD3Vlk6hdZAeQyq4o-QZy

Tapu and Gogi are having a blast staying together and having lots of fun! But it seems Jetha is facing some trouble listening to them creating havoc at his house. Even in the morning when he wishes to use the bathroom, he finds himself locked out!

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Shailesh Lodha
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #livcomedy

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

Jetha से पहले Tapu और Gogi ने किया Bathroom पे कब्ज़ा | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Sangram Ke Aam
